<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Importing Images</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading2_atoc_"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Importing Images</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To import an image, select </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="ImportEdit_Bitmap_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">File|Import Image...</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to display the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="ImportEdit_Bitmap_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Import Image</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box (fig. </text><conditional-text type="IF" value="CHM,HLP,HXS,HTML,DEMO,USER1,USER2,USER3"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">89</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">44</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">). </text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> Then click the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Select Image</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button and select the image to import. For the purposes of this exercise, the image used is unimportant. Identify several locations on the image with known real-world coordinates and click on them. A dialog box will appear in which to specify the real-world coordinates. For this example, click on the upper left corner of the image and set X = 0 and Y = 0.  Then click on the lower right corner and set X = 1000 and Y = -1000. When at least two sets of coordinates have been specified, the user can click the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button to finish importing the bitmap. The image will be plotted at the specified location.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Image Caption" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px; tabstops:none;"><table rowcount="2" colcount="1" style="cell-padding:0px; cell-spacing:0px; page-break-inside:avoid; border-width:0px; cell-border-width:0px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="ImportBitmap.bmp" scale="60.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">See caption</title></image></para>
        </td>
